---
title: Peppercorn Lamb Rump & Spiced Veggie Fries with Tomato Salad & Mayo
description: You know you’re in for a good night when the only thing standing between you and this classy lamb dish is a matter of minutes.
With only the most tender lamb rump cut, a punchy pepper crusting and baked veggie fries, you just can't go wrong.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
